> scriptural reference could be found out

Parasara mentioned making offerings to Shiva in fire with "tryambakam 
yajaamahe" mantra (Mrityunjaya mantra) as a remedy to several horoscopic 
problems!!

Vishnu Dharmottara Purana mentioned Rudra Yajna. Agni Purana also 
mentioned Rudra homam. Mrityunjaya homam to Shiva with Mrityunjaya 
mantra is also mentioned and popular in tradition.

*        *        *

